wikipedia_page.main: James "Jay" Bell (born 24 November 1989) is an English footballer who  last played for Marine. He also previously played for Accrington Stanley for three years and made his Football League debut on 26 April 2008 in a 3–1 win over Wrexham. In August 2009, he joined Welsh Premier League side Bala Town, making three appearances before moving to Marine.
